        <Parent_String>Anatolian pottery styles [300107545], Anatolian (culture or style) [300019755], Near Eastern (Early Western World) [300019571], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
